4 FOR the purpose of requiring the Maryland Department of Health to inspect assisted living
5 programs located in Prince George’s County on a certain basis; requiring the
6 Department to publish a report of each inspection on the Department’s website
7 within a certain time period and provide the report to the Prince George’s County
8 Council; and generally relating to inspections of assisted living programs in Prince
9 George’s County.
